BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260515T060000
DTEND:20260515T084800
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.055ft at 06:00\n-2.925ft at 08:48\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 <strong>Dawn to 10:00AM:</strong> Holding blend of SSW Southern Hemi and s
 horter-period WNW swell maintains waist to shoulder high+ surf at many spo
 ts\, as top breaks go overhead on sets. Favorable early morning tide push 
 with clean conditions. Deepening high tides later morning.\n\n<strong>Afte
 rnoon Outlook:</strong> Conditions are set to stay pretty clean all aftern
 oon for spots in town. Mid-PM lower tide window is the next best after the
  AM tide push\, slowing down again in the evening.
END:VEVENT
