BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260516T071800
DTEND:20260516T094800
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.106ft at 07:18\n-2.925ft at 09:48\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Blend of SSW Southern Hemi and shorter-period WNW swell tops out\, with wi
 despread waist to shoulder high+ waves\, while standouts hit a foot overhe
 ad. Draining negative low tide for the dawn patrol\, then incoming tide pu
 sh helps first half of the morning. Mid day and later afternoon/evening hi
 gh tides tend to slow tide sensitive breaks. \n\nLight/variable morning wi
 nds\, then possible offshore NW flow for town spots in the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
