BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260518T091800
DTEND:20260518T115400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.048ft at 09:18\n-2.995ft at 11:54\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Blend of SSW swell and NW swell tapers off\, with mainly waist-chest high 
 waves in the morning\, dipping in the afternoon. \n\nDraining negative low
  tide for the dawn patrol\, then incoming tide push lends a hand much of t
 he morning. Early afternoon high tide bogs down tide sensitive spots. Ligh
 t/variable winds through the morning\, expected to turn light SW over the 
 afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
